product.title: FAMKIT Travel Carrying Case Compatible for Complete Styler and Attachments, Portable Organizer Box Storage Bag with Hanging Hook for Hair Curler Accessories Tools, Black
product.description:
"Features:

The carry case measures 12.2x5x6"", compatible with Dyson Airwrap Styler and attachments.

It has 4 divided padded slots, 1 clear zippered pocket, 1 open pouch to keep your kit organized.

Made from polyester fabric, this travel carry case for Dyson is tear resistant and durable.

Thick pad design provides excellent protection against bumps and scratches.

With strong hook, you can hang it on the wall and leave the bag open.

Specification:

Item name: Travel case for Dyson Airwrap Styler

Color: Black

Material: Polyester

Product size: 31x12.5x15cm / 12.2x5x6""

Note:

Please allow 1-3cm (0.4-1.18"") difference due to manual measurement and slight color variation for different display setting.

Package Includes:

1 * Hair Dryer Storage Bag

"

Product size: 31x12.5x15cm / 12.2x5x6""

Note:

Please allow 1-3cm (0.4-1.18"") difference due to manual measurement and slight color variation for different display setting.

Package Includes:

1 * Hair Dryer Storage Bag

" * Effective Protection : Made from polyester fabric, this travel carry case for Dyson is tear resistant and durable. with padded interior, it protects your expensive Dyson hair tools from scratches, bumps, and dust.
 * Customized Compartments : This storage case is perfect for organizing and protecting your Dyson hair curling accessories during travel. It has 4 divided slots that fit your styler, barrels, brushes, and dryer. The well-padded design keeps everything in place and prevents them from knocking against each other. The extra flap separates the styler and cable, ensuring they stay in place and preventing scratches.
 * Clever Design : Portable travel organizer bag with double way zippers,Metal hook for easy access and hanging. With strong hook, you can hang it on the wall and leave the bag open.
 * Convenient to Use : Keep your kits organized with this premium storage holder case. Its durable and smooth zipper, along with the stylish golden two-zip design, ensures easy access. Hang it conveniently with the interior hook on bathroom doors, towel bars, and more. The lightweight design and top handle make it perfect for travel. A great gift for loved ones.
 * Make Travel Easier : This dyson airwrap travel case for hair tools is a perfect gift for birthdays, anniversaries, and Christmas. It has compact dimensions of 12.2x5x6 inches . Its lightweight design ensures it won't take up much space in your luggage, making it ideal for travel.
